NAME
    Filesys::Virtual - Perl extension to provide a framework for a virtual
    filesystem

SYNOPSIS
      use Filesys::Virtual;

DESCRIPTION
    This is a base class. See "SEE ALSO" below.

  EXPORT
    None by default.

